description:
This week we recap the beginning of the #RHONY Cartagena trip, plus the #RHOC season premiere, the Southern Charm finale, and more. Plus Thomas John (Lifetime's Seatbelt Psychic) stops by to make some predictions about the Housewives and more.


*For bonus episodes, join the Patreon atPatreon.com/EverythingIconic
